Package: cricketdata
Version: 0.0.3
Title: International Cricket Data
Description: Data on all international cricket matches is provided by ESPNCricinfo.
  This package provides some scraper functions to download the data
  into tibbles ready for analysis. Some innings-level data sourced from Howzstat
  is also included in the package.
